OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FIt will be generally sunny
OL,6,Fand warm, though cooler on south
OL,7,Ffacing coasts. Windy in the southwest
OL,8,Fand around the coasts. Turning
OL,9,Fcloudier with rain spreading east
OL,10,Fthrough the evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,13,FSomewhat cloudy Wednesday morning but
OL,14,Fbright spells developing, dry and
OL,15,Fbright by day. Cooler with sunshine
OL,16,Fand showers on Thursday. Turning wet
OL,17,Fand windy on Friday, especially in the
OL,18,Fwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
